T 有了巨大的改进 OpenAI 官方称，ChatGPT 是在人类的帮助下创建并训练的，人类训练师对该 AI 早期版本回答查询的方式进行排名和评级。然后，这些信息被反馈到系统中，系统会根据训练师的偏好来调整答案——这是一种训练人工智能的标准方法，被称为强化学习。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-79fec1e24aa644b22b05e3e11cfcbf34_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "142 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/581304464"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIpb/I4KifqvwvEAMaCDkxNDYwNDc0IOy43Z4GMAQ43gRADnIJNTgxMzA0NDY0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1675156115.825556", "card_id": "Q_518983086", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 202}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "俄罗斯进攻乌克兰为什么不一开始就全军压上，狮子搏兔，反而在战事不顺的时候继续增兵？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-dba37b09a166d8f2c786832d85f40fb5_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "136 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/518983086"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIpb/I4KifqvwvEAMaCDc3NjExMzY0IPbO65AGMA446wNAD3IJNTE4OTgzMDg2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1675156115.8261364", "card_id": "Q_572743422", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 67}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "对讲机为什么还没被手机取代？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "手机现在通话这么方便，为什么还有对讲机的存在？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-1913b1f6070822b265bd1fb2381ba443_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "130 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/572743422"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Ipb/I4KifqvwvE